responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "AB94858541C15AB9D6D3DABDD68DAA2B", "I nodded in agreement. \"This world has so much potential for the future.\" \"It does indeed!\" he agreed, wholeheartedly. I said my goodbyes, assuring Vagesh that I would return to see what amazing things he and Kish might create. He thanked me for my interest, shook my hand enthusiastically, then ducked back into the tent, whistling happily as he returned to his work. As I headed across the settlement, I heard Kish\'s muffled voice emerging from the tent and smiled.\"You whistle too much!\" she hissed. \"Can\'t make chemical magic with so much whistling!\"")
